LIBRARY MANAGEMENT SYSTEM USING C
Objective:
To develop a simple Library Management System using C programming language
Introduction:
This program is used to manage library books,it allows the user to add books,display books,search books,issue books,and return books
Source Code:
The source code of this project is available in the file libraryManagement.c
Output:
Library Management System menu will be displayed and the user can perform operations like add, display,search,issue and return books
